snippet.title: Version 1.1 Trailer - "The Theft of The Rimet Cup" | Reverse: 1999
snippet.description:
The hall of the Rimet Cup Exhibition has seen many sensational news stories today.
There were the rampaging rock pirate, the spotlight-seeking artist, the solitude-craving border collie ... and the Great Thief and her dramatic entrance. 

Grab your popcorn, love.
The show is about to begin.

Version 1.1 of #Reverse1999, The Theft of The Rimet Cup, will be available on Nov 9 on Mobile and PC. 
Download Now: https://bit.ly/RimetCupYouTube
